eu.cassandra.sim.math.response
Class PricingVector

java.lang.Object
  eu.cassandra.sim.math.response.PricingVector

public class PricingVector
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used for implementing an array of pricings that are a result of the analysis of the available pricing schemes (Basic and New). The array is then used as an input to the Response Models creation procedure.

Version:
0.9, Date: 29.07.2013
Author:
Antonios Chrysopoulos
